** Masculine inanimate nouns ending in a soft consonant (&quot;c, č, ď, dz, dž, j, ľ, ň, š, ť, ž&quot;), e.g. (&quot;remote&quot;) → (&quot;about the remote&quot;), 
** Feminine nouns ending in a soft consonant or a soft consonant followed by &quot;a&quot;, e.g. , (&quot;bone&quot;) → (&quot;about bone&quot;)
** Feminine nouns ending in -ia or -ea, e.g. 
