** Some masculine singular nouns, e.g. [* In a few cases, a vowel change may occur, e.g. ó → o, or a vowel may be dropped. ** Final consonants in Wrocław and Bytom used to be soft, which is still reflected in suffixed forms, hence -i-.]
** All neuter singular nouns ending in , e.g. 
** Some neuter singular nouns ending in , e.g. 
